        if (req_capsule_get_size(pill, &RMF_EADATA, RCL_CLIENT) < size) {
                rc = sptlrpc_cli_enlarge_reqbuf(req, &RMF_EADATA, size);
                if (rc) {
<4>[ 1276.381690] Free repbuf early: reqlen=600 replen=688
<4>[ 1276.393285] EADATA size 65528/80
<4>[ 1276.393308] Free repbuf early: reqlen=600 replen=688

There are two solutions:
1. free and realloc the request buffer for EA (shrinking it).
2. Set a smaller request buffer for EA: i.e. limit the maximum value of EA size in the request buffer of 4096
